## Available Skills

> **This file is intentionally a stub.** The active skill index renders directly inside
> `~/.claude/CLAUDE.md` (and any other consumer) by reading `distributions/skills-registry.json`
> from the local `a-i--skills` clone at chezmoi-render time. See
> `private_dot_claude/CLAUDE.md.tmpl` for the inlined template logic.
>
> Earlier attempt to host the dynamic logic in this file failed because chezmoi's `include`
> function reads file contents as raw text — it does not recursively process included files
> as templates. The logic now lives at the call site instead.

Canonical source of truth: `~/Workspace/{{ .organvm_dir }}/{{ .skills_dir }}/distributions/skills-registry.json`.
